sg":"<blockquote>點解要特別提到港大生<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n傳媒習慣，讀書果班會突顯U/IVE/失學"},{"pid":"2811093c2ffc12badbef045d6662abc44d44ec7a","tid":341804,"uid":115451,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-31T07:53:41.000Z","msg":"仲未死人 唔夠轟動 嚇唔到啲傻鳩咖<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/10.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4307f59f269be19833ae9e9a56b8502f1c87142b","tid":341804,"uid":75765,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-31T08:15:04.000Z","msg":"蕉徑去營盤都未上山， 唔知算好彩定唔好彩&hellip;&hellip;"},{"pid":"808a1c0f58b17d8584e5412379cd28d67a1cdae2","tid":341804,"uid":46086,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-31T08:16:04.000Z","msg":"渣ga"}]}